🐾 Happy National Black Cat Day! 🐾

Did you know black cats often face unfair treatment due to myths and superstitions? These sleek sweethearts are just as loving and deserving of homes 🖤 Let’s break the stigma and show them the care they deserve!

Got a black cat that rules your world? Snap a picture of your furry friend and tag us to spotlight these stunning beauties. Let’s flood the feed with all the black cat love today! 

#NationalBlackCatDay #LoveBlackCats #OnCloudCanine #CloudCanineCrew #FearFreeCertified #PetSitting #AkronOH #PawsomePets

It's World Animal Enrichment Day! 🌍 🐾

Did you know that mental and physical enrichment can make a world of difference for your dog’s well-being? Providing your dog with enrichment activities helps reduce anxiety, prevent boredom, and may even curb unwanted behaviors. By keeping their minds active, you're also supporting their happiness and health! 

Let's celebrate by adding a little more enrichment into our furry friends’ routines—because they deserve the best! 💕 

#WorldAnimalEnrichmentDay #OnCloudCanine #HappyPets #FearFreeCertified #CloudCanineCrew #AkronOH #PawsomePets #EnrichmentforDogs

November is National Senior Pet Month 💛 🐾 

At On Cloud Canine, we understand that senior pets need extra love and attention, and we’re here to provide just that! From gentle walks to extra snuggles, our team makes sure your pet is well cared for and comfortable. Let's celebrate our wise, wonderful senior sweethearts who bring so much love and loyalty to our lives!

#SeniorPetLove #OnCloudCanine #NationalSeniorPetMonth #GoldenYears #FurEverYoung #FearFreePets #AkronOH #CloudCanineCrew

✨ HAPPY HOWLOWEEN ✨ Join us at daycare the week of October 28th to enter your pup into our Costume Contest!

We’re excited to announce some delicious new additions to our lunch menu that are sure to make your furry friends wag their tails! Introducing our Seasonal Barkuterie Board and Pumpkin Pupsicle!

🍽️ Barkuterie Board: Imagine a charcuterie board designed just for dogs! Our Barkuterie Board is a colorful assortment of tasty, pup-friendly delights, including:
* Cheeses like cottage cheese with a sweet addition of honey
* Savory Meats like freeze-dried lamb liver cubes
* Yummy Veggies like bite-sized bell peppers and butternut squash
* Fruity Treats like a serving of applesauce with a cinnamon garnish
* Delicious Dairy such as plain greek yogurt or goats’ milk blended with pumpkin and frozen to delight your pups taste buds

🍂 Pumpkin Pupsicle: Cool off this fall with our refreshing Pumpkin Pupsicle! Made with pureed pumpkin, carrots, and plain greek yogurt, these frozen treats are not only delicious but also packed with nutrients. Perfect for a warm day or as a special treat after playtime!

Both of these options are made with love and care, ensuring they’re safe and nutritious for your furry companions. We can’t wait for your pups to dig in!

When are they available? Starting Wednesday, October 2nd, the Barkuterie Board and Pumpkin Pupsicle will be available every day during lunch. Be sure to sign your pup up for a treat they’ll love!

#oncloudcanine #oncloudcaninecrew #dogdaycare #doggydaycare #fearfreepets #akronohio #barkuterie #pupsicle
